1
00:00:09,480 --> 00:00:10,960
(PHONE RINGING)

2
00:00:39,120 --> 00:00:40,520
Hello?

3
00:00:41,080 --> 00:00:43,080
He's not there. Who's speaking?

4
00:00:43,280 --> 00:00:44,920
(INSECT BUZZING)

5
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:47,080
Sorry, the Prince of where?

6
00:00:47,400 --> 00:00:48,800
Which one?

7
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:51,600
No, no. No, which prince?
Not which Wales.

8
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:53,360
Um...

9
00:00:53,720 --> 00:00:56,480
-What year is this?
-I think that's probably for me!

10
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:58,640
Hold this.

11
00:01:00,400 --> 00:01:03,960
Hello? Ah, yes, everything's fine.
Don't worry.

12
00:01:04,360 --> 00:01:06,240
Well, exactly.
Why should you be worrying?

13
00:01:06,720 --> 00:01:08,120
Who even mentioned worrying?

14
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:10,880
She's fine. No, your mum is fine.

15
00:01:10,960 --> 00:01:12,520
Don't answer this phone.
I answer this phone.

16
00:01:12,600 --> 00:01:14,200
-Where have you been?
-Party. Just a party.

17
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:16,120
Um, yes, your mum is here, actually,

18
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:17,760
but she can't come to the phone
at the moment.

19
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:19,960
Well, she's busy.

20
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:21,960
Oh, you know, the Commonwealth.

21
00:01:22,080 --> 00:01:24,520
It's your son, ma'am,
he wants to talk to you.

22
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:25,880
We can't let him see you like this,

23
00:01:25,960 --> 00:01:27,240
well, hear you,
not that he could hear you,

24
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:28,920
-you're a fish.
-(PHONE RINGS)

25
00:01:29,320 --> 00:01:31,120
Sorry, I've got another call coming in.

26
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:32,400
Hello?

27
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:35,920
There is not a bit of use
yelling, ambassador.

28
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:38,240
Your warrior chief is trapped
in my Tardis.

29
00:01:38,360 --> 00:01:41,120
And until you've turned Her Majesty
here back into a human being,

30
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:43,880
he's staying put. Don't worry,
he's perfectly safe...

31
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:48,320
Just popping you on hold.

32
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:58,840
What have you done?

33
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:02,120
I thought that it was a fly.

34
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:05,680
So much for the slaughter
of 10 billion souls.

35
00:02:06,240 --> 00:02:08,640
-What is going on?
-I was at a party.

36
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:10,400
There was a slight incident.

37
00:02:10,640 --> 00:02:12,720
What, so you sneak out
at night to parties?

38
00:02:12,920 --> 00:02:14,880
Hang on. You're dressed up.
You never dress up.

39
00:02:15,600 --> 00:02:18,360
-Was River at the party?
-Oh, why would she be there?

40
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:20,480
Don't... Just don't lie to me, Doctor.

41
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:23,240
-You're rubbish at it.
-Look, I do not sneak out at night

42
00:02:23,320 --> 00:02:25,280
to parties with-with-with River Song.

43
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:27,960
-Hmm, how is she?
-Fine.

44
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:29,600
-See? Rubbish.
-Oh!

45
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:31,520
Look, sorry, but I am in
the middle of a thing.

46
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,640
Doctor!

47
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,400
Doctor.

48
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,680
I... I need to talk to you.

49
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:47,640
There is a reason that I couldn't sleep.

50
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:52,320
-Rory!
-What are you doing?

51
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,400
You've got the serious face on.

52
00:02:53,480 --> 00:02:55,360
I always shout for Rory
when you've got the serious face.

53
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:57,560
Rory, she's having an emotion!

54
00:02:57,680 --> 00:03:00,320
-What? What's wrong, Amy?
-Why are you calling him?

55
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,400
It's his turn.

56
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:04,000
You two have... You two have turns?

57
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,480
No!

58
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:11,120
It's the wrong fish.
I've taken the wrong fish.

59
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:13,240
River, we've got the wrong fish.

60
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:16,000
Look, sorry, you two.
I've made a mistake.

61
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:17,440
I've got three hours to save
the Commonwealth.

62
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:20,200
What happens in three hours?

63
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,880
The pet shops open.

